msgid ""
"<1.so>The <2.se_co>Great Calamity <3.re_co>was a catastrophe\n"
"that...contaminated <4.se_co>Hyrule Castle<5.re_co>.<6.pa> That's\n"
"how I understood it, anyway.\n"
"Our world was once filled with beautiful\n"
"cities and prosperous villages, but the\n"
"<7.se_co>Calamity<8.re_co> destroyed all of that.\n"
"Luckily, Hateno Village was far enough\n"
"away from <9.se_co>Hyrule Castle<10.re_co> that the damage\n"
"here was minor in comparison.\n"
"And then there was something about a\n"
"brave soul that tried to stop the <11.se_co>Calamity<12.re_co>,\n"
"I think...\n"
"<13.so>I don't remember it all. What does it\n"
"matter, though? That's all in the past."
msgstr ""

